THAC0:  +3
Damage type:  missile (piercing)
Launcher:  Bow~

@650109 = ~Arrow +4~
@650110 = ~These arrows were enchanted through magical means when they were created.  Each is much straighter than the average arrow, and will leave a bow string effortlessly to streak toward a target with deadly accuracy.

STATISTICS:

