@650491 = ~Crowley's Axe~
@650492 = ~The history of this weapon is not known.  It was given to you by Crowley, a backwater ranger who desired it to be resharpened.  You did so, and are to bring the axe to him in the woodlands north of Amn.  This particular axe gives its user a bonus to his armor class, allows the wielder to use the blade with mastery of the axe proficiency, as well as provides a number of specific resistances to damage types: Poison, Fire, Cold, Acid, and Electrical.

