@650540 = ~The flight arrow, as its name implies, is built for distance.  These are lightweight arrows and are often used for hunting.  Most of these arrows are made of ash or birch and are 30 to 40 inches long.   These arrows are tipped with silver, making them effective against lycanthropes, undead, and other monsters that are not normally affected by arrows.

