@650543 = ~Fencing Cloak~
@650544 = ~Standard fencing cloaks are worn by many swordsmen who enjoy its loose and voluminous folds which can entangle a weapon in the thick cloth.  This cloak provides a bit of protection against slashing and piercing weapons that have a chance of becoming "stuck" in the heavy cloak.

