THAC0:  +4
Special:
  +12 Hit Points While Equipped
  Maximum Damage with Successful Attack
Damage type:  slashing
Weight: 6
Speed Factor: 4
Proficiency Type:  Two Handed Sword
Type:  2-handed

Usable By:
